         <abstract id="aspace_2d9d171a2a41643a5512118c4a462b09">The records consist of correspondence, news releases, publications, a press book, and letters congratulating Yale on its 250th anniversary.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_2c41b55eb98ff302b5b55302a6303d31">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 2-A (YRG 2-A), Records of the Yale president's office.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_ebae942e74f0bc6dfdfc22701b2261d0">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Office of the President, 1951.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_346c6261073d5fb8efb65ef84eb851d1">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_631e68e1cc0dddf315fdc789d878514e">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>250th Anniversary Commemoration, Yale University, Records (RU 48). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <processinfo id="aspace_65d82fef6a6ce94d9e1e742855a9563a">
         <head>Processing Information</head>
         <p>Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.</p>  
      </processinfo>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_732ff1d65f361f24ed6bd196c11bf864">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, news releases, publications, a press book, and letters congratulating Yale on its 250th anniversary.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
